data.name: xenaMC
data.description:
xenaMC is a server filled with gamemodes and minigames!


survival - its in the name bro

skywars - get the best loot possible and get to the middle to defeat every single player to win!

skyblock - choose from 1 of 3 island types and use your survival skills to build and expand your island!

bedwars - defend your bed and destroy other teams beds. be the last team standing to win!

Pit PVP - hop into a pit to fight other players, grind levels and gold and upgrade to beat more players! upgrades are fair for all players.
